highlights.text: Ed Sheeran has the most spots on Top Songs Global. “River (feat. Ed Sheeran)” is the highest at #4.
“One Dance” by Drake, WizKid, and Kyla is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Global, up 108 spots at #84.
“IDGAF” by Dua Lipa is the highest new entry on Top Songs Global at #120.
“Closer” by The Chainsmokers and Halsey has been on Top Songs Global the longest, at 54 weeks straight.
